attention to his physical and psychological 
integrity, as well as any other allegation such 
as &#8220;torture to obtain confession&#8221; or arrested in 
relation with their peaceful activities in 
defence of human rights are baseless. 
</p>
<p>The Constitution provides for the punishment 
of those who commit acts of mistreatment 
and torture. Legal provisions have also been 
made for the legal protection of the victims. </p>

