families of the detainees were not able to see 
them during the investigative phase, and only 
saw them at the trial.  
</p>
<p>The detainees were reportedly subjected to 
torture at the moment of detention, during their 
transfers, at the pre-trial facilities o the State 
Committee of National Security and at the pre-
trial facility No. 5 of the Ministry of Justice. 
</p>
