him. On 5 December, the Bishkek May Day 
district procurator's office received notice of 
action taken by Mr. Kuleshov against the 
police officers who detained him. The notice 
was reviewed by the procurator and no 
charges were brought against them for lack of 
evidence. A review by the procurator did not 
yield any evidence of violations or of </p>

