detention. No investigation into the cause of 
death has been conducted, nobody has been 
prosecuted in relation to the allegations of 
</p>
<p>By letter dated 19/03/09, the Government 
indicated that Mr. Damiran Enkhbat had been 
sentenced six times and in 2004 and 
sentenced to three years in prison. On August 
