Central hospital of the Judicial Decision 
Enforcement Authority, doctors carefully 
discussed Mr. Damiran&#8217;s health condition and 
unanimously decided to submit a release-
from-prison proposal to the Prosecutor&#8217;s 
Office of the Capital city and the Court of 
Khan-Uul district. </p>

