filed at that time. Later that day, they were taken 
to the Office of the Prosecutor, where they were 
charged on three counts of attempted murder, 
illegal possession of explosives and firearms. 
</p>
<p>Prior to the arrest, Mr. Limcumpao, Mr. 
Alcantara and Mr. Bathan had been planning to 
