of Mr. Tibuleac&#8217;s death proved that the 
circumstances of his death are not linked to 
the demonstrations. There were also cases 
where defenders complained of ill-treatment 
by the police. In the course of the 
investigations, the respective persons 
declared that they had not been ill-treated, did 
not suffer physical injuries and did not ask for 
a lawyer. 
