dd.1 
</b></p>
<p><b>338</b> Para Country Date Type Mandate Allegations transmitted Government response 
and abscesses; keloid scar formation; damage to 
the urethra resulting in urinary incontinence; 
painful sexual intercourse; and sexual 
dysfunction.  
</p>
<p>In addition, despite the commonness of FGM/C, 
health providers (traditional and modern) and 
the women themselves are often poorly 
equipped to handle the resulting complications, 
especially those associated with pregnancy, and 
the physical and psychological sexual 
dysfunctions. 
