right ear, and treated her regularly throughout 
her time in detention. Ms. Tayfur was 
diagnosed as suffering from diabetes, 
rheumatoid arthritis pain and chest pains. She 
also had a condition known as &#8220;Aleppo boil&#8221; </p>

