64/71 prison, given that he had committed a 
gross violation of the custody regime at the 
UAa-64/80 prison and had left the grounds 
without permission. Upon his arrival at the 
UYa-64/71 facility, he underwent a medical 
examination. The facility where Mr. Z. is 
now serving his prison term has no inmates 
with tuberculosis. 
