clenched fists and heavy boots by a ZRP officer. 
On 2 January 2009, Andrew Chimanga was 
assaulted by officers of the Murehwa police. He 
was beaten on the soles, hands and head. On 11 
January, Last Muzadzi was exposed to extreme 
cold temperatures by ZRP officers at Dorowa 
Police station. On 15 January, Andrew Maraire 
